ground_truth:
Because $\triangle ABC \sim \triangle DEF,$ we know that: \begin{align*}
\frac{EF}{ED} &= \frac{BC}{BA} \\
\frac{EF}{3\text{ cm}} &= \frac{8\text{ cm}}{5\text{ cm}} \\
EF &= \frac{8\text{ cm}\cdot3\text{ cm}}{5\text{ cm}} = \boxed{4.8}\text{ cm}.
\end{align*}

